## Step 1: First, let's improve the PDF generator to include line numbers and proper line wrappingI understand that you're having issues with your codebase to PDF program. Let's fix the immediate problems and enhance the PDF output to include line numbers and proper line breaks ("ZeilenumbrÃ¼che").

